Clean Willy can.

52:32.852 --> 52:37.356
Oh, my! I think I'm going to die.

52:45.364 --> 52:47.950
Where is he?

54:17.336 --> 54:20.588
Good heavens! He's
in a right bad state.

54:20.589 --> 54:22.632
